Feature: Edit profile of registered user in http://elearningm1.upskills.in/

Scenario: Launch Registration page
Given Website is launched
When User clicks on Sign up button
Then Registration page is opened

Scenario: Next button is displayed after successful registration
Given Registration page is launched
When User fills up all the mandatory fields
And Click on Registration button
Then Registration successful and next button is displayed

Scenario: Launch Edit Profile page
Given After succussful registration Next button is visible
When Click on Next button
Then Click on Homepage button
And Click on Edit Profile button
And User is navigated to Edit Profile page

Scenario: User is able to edit fields in Edit Profile page
Given User is on Edit Profile page
When User edits First name, Last name and Phone number
And Click on Save settings button
Then Profile changes are saved successfully 

